    "long_instructions": "## Upload an Image\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to describe an image.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Include the image you just looked at as part of your chat.\r\n2. **Copy and paste** the following prompt: \r\n\r\n>Describe this image. List as many things as you can notice in the image.\r\n\r\n3. Press **Send**.\r\n4. Then read **AI Chat's response** and compare it to your own.\r\n5. Complete the **\"What's in an image?\"** and **\"Privacy and Ethical Concerns\"** sections in your Unit Guide.\r\n\r\n",
